tern. Schließlich werden dem Entscheider konkrete Handlungsunterstützungen an die Hand gegeben.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 15. Jun 2019) 4aComplex environments. 4aDecision Support Tools. 4aUmfeldkomplexität. 4abusiness decisions. 4adecision support tools. 4aunternehmerische Entscheidungen. 70(DE-601)1046653270(DE-588)4061963-1aUnternehmen2gnd 70(DE-601)1051605200(DE-588)4202171-6aEntscheidungsunterstützung2gnd 70(DE-601)1058294200(DE-588)4113446-1aEntscheidungsfindung2gnd 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Management.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG OWV ebook Paket Lehrbücher Wirtschaftswiss. 2017z9783110549201oZDB-23-OLW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2017z9783110540550oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Economics 2017z9783110547740oZDB-23-DBV0 cEPUBz97831105184430 cprintz978311051819140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110518207423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110518207.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA14ALL  aPDA15STM  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2HUM  aPDA3STM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DBVb2017  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-OLWb2017